'''华为Mate 40系列'''是[[华为|华为]]公司于2020年10月22日发布的5G[[平板手机|平板手机]]系列，包括'''Mate 40'''、'''Mate 40 Pro'''、'''Mate 40 Pro+'''和'''Mate 40 RS保时捷设计'''<ref>{{Cite web |title=华为Mate 40系列国行发布：4999元起售，最高售价13999元_科技_腾讯网 |url=https://tech.qq.com/a/20201030/012566.htm |access-date=2022-01-26 |work=tech.qq.com |archive-date=2022-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220209005442/https://tech.qq.com/a/20201030/012566.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Mate 40系列采用与[[華為P40系列|華為P40系列]]相似的正面左上挖孔布局<ref>{{Cite web|title=华为Mate40/Mate40 Pro背部渲染图曝光 或有Pro+版本|url=https://tech.sina.cn/mobile/xp/2020-08-21/detail-iivhvpwy2179642.d.html|access-date=2022-03-24|date=2020-08-21|last=|work=[[新浪科技|新浪科技]]}}</ref>，搭载基于5納米制程的麒麟9000系列[[SoC|SoC]]芯片<ref>{{Cite web|title=巅峰即绝版？华为史上最强手机发布 5纳米芯片集成153亿个晶体管|url=https://finance.sina.com.cn/wm/2020-10-22/doc-iiznezxr7528550.shtml|access-date=2022-03-24|date=2020-10-22|work=新浪財經}}</ref>。

而在2020年10月发布会后，华为在随后的时间内陆续以直接上架、发布会等的形式推出了几款Mate 40系列手机。2021年3月10日，华为发布了Mate 40E 5G手机，其搭载麒麟990E 5G芯片，主摄更换为6400万像素摄像头<ref name=":3">{{Cite web |title=Huawei Mate 40E 5G announced with Kirin 990E and 90Hz curved screen, Mate 40 RS Porsche Design gets a new variant |url=https://www.gsmarena.com/huawei_mate_40e_5g_specs_price_sale_date-news-48133.php |access-date=2021-03-11 |work=GSMArena |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312114937/https://www.gsmarena.com/huawei_mate_40e_5g_specs_price_sale_date-news-48133.php |archive-date=2021-03-12 |dead-url=no |quote=The Mate 40E 5G's rear panel houses a circular camera island that includes a 64MP primary. }}</ref>，随后在2021年6月29日，发布了该机型的4G版本<ref name=":13">{{Cite web |title=Huawei Mate 40E 4G - Specs, Price, Reviews, and Best Deals |url=https://www.gizmochina.com/product/huawei-mate-40e-4g/ |access-date=2022-02-28 |work=Gizmochina |language=en-US}}</ref>。2021年4月23日，华为在其官网上架了Mate 40 Pro的4G版本<ref>{{Cite web |title=HUAWEI Mate 40 Pro 4G版 |url=https://consumer.huawei.com/cn/phones/mate40-pro-4g/ |access-date=2021-05-15 |work=华为消费者官网 |language=zh-CN |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423065505/https://consumer.huawei.com/cn/phones/mate40-pro-4g/ |archive-date=2021-04-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其处理器亦为麒麟9000，但不支持5G网络，其是首部预装搭载[[鸿蒙OS|鸿蒙OS 2.0]]的手机<ref>{{Cite web |title=Huawei Mate 40 Pro 4G could be first phone with HarmonyOS, reveals TENAA listing |url=https://www.gizmochina.com/2021/04/26/huawei-mate-40-pro-4g-could-be-first-phone-with-harmonyos-reveals-tenaa-listing/ |access-date=2021-05-15 |date=2021-04-26 |last=Valiyathara |first=Anvinraj |work=Gizmochina |language=en-US |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210428173521/https://www.gizmochina.com/2021/04/26/huawei-mate-40-pro-4g-could-be-first-phone-with-harmonyos-reveals-tenaa-listing/ |archive-date=2021-04-28 |dead-url=no |quote=To be precise, the TENAA listing states that the Mate 40 Pro 4G is equipped with the latest HarmonyOS 2.0. }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Huawei Mate 40 Pro 4G with pre-built HarmonyOS passes 3C certificate featuring 66W charger |url=https://www.huaweicentral.com/huawei-mate-40-pro-4g-with-pre-built-harmonyos-passes-3c-certificate-featuring-66w-charger/ |access-date=2021-05-15 |date=2021-04-27 |last=Sarkar |first=Amy |work=Huawei Central |language=en-US |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210427064118/https://www.huaweicentral.com/huawei-mate-40-pro-4g-with-pre-built-harmonyos-passes-3c-certificate-featuring-66w-charger/ |archive-date=2021-04-27 |dead-url=no |quote=On the other hand, it was reported due to US restrictions on Huawei, the American-based companies aren’t able to supply 5G equipment to the company. So, Huawei keeps the processor still the same Kirin 9000…… }}</ref>。2022年2月28日，华为在其官网上架了搭载麒麟9000L芯片的Mate 40E Pro手机<ref name=":11">{{Cite web |title=HUAWEI Mate 40E Pro 5G - 华为官网 |url=https://consumer.huawei.com/cn/phones/mate40e-pro/ |access-date=2022-02-28 |work=consumer.huawei.com |language=zh-CN}}</ref><ref name="huaweicentral-mate40epro">{{Cite web |title=Huawei Mate 40E Pro with Kirin 9000L 5G hexa-core processor launched |url=https://www.huaweicentral.com/huawei-mate-40e-pro-with-kirin-9000l-5g-hexa-core-processor-launched/ |access-date=2022-02-28 |date=2022-02-28 |last=Li |first=Deng |work=Huawei Central |language=en-US}}</ref>。

== 设计 ==
[[File:Huawei_Mate_40_Pro_Front.jpg|缩略图]]

Mate 40系列正面均采用曲面屏，而除了Mate 40 RS保时捷设计外的该系列手机背面均采用官方称为“星环”式的摄像头布局<ref>{{Cite web |title=华为Mate 40系列发布：后背星环设计 屏幕90Hz刷新率 |url=https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2020-10-22/doc-iiznezxr7510052.shtml |access-date=2021-06-21 |date=2020-10-22 |work=[[新浪|新浪财经]] |quote=华为消费者业务CEO余承东首先介绍了Mate 40和Mate 40 Pro。后置相机系统采用星环设计…… |archive-date=2021-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210624202726/https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2020-10-22/doc-iiznezxr7510052.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Mate 40 RS保时捷设计的机身背面则采用官方称为“星钻设计”的摄像头排布<ref>{{Cite web |title=HUAWEI Mate 40 RS 保时捷设计 |url=https://consumer.huawei.com/cn/phones/porsche-design-mate40-rs/ |access-date=2021-06-21 |work=华为消费者官网 |language=zh-CN |quote=标志性星钻设计镜头，…… |archive-date=2021-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210623075706/https://consumer.huawei.com/cn/phones/porsche-design-mate40-rs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=The Porsche Design Huawei Mate 40 RS launches for a whopping €2295! |url=https://www.gizmochina.com/2020/10/22/the-porsche-design-huawei-mate-40-rs-launches-for-a-whopping-e2295/ |access-date=2020-10-24 |date=2020-10-22 |last=Onawole |first=Habeeb |work=Gizmochina |language=en-US |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101061705/https://www.gizmochina.com/2020/10/22/the-porsche-design-huawei-mate-40-rs-launches-for-a-whopping-e2295/ |archive-date=2020-11-01 |dead-url=no |quote=The stand out part of the design is the octagonal camera housing,…… }}</ref>。

Mate 40的正面曲面屏弧度为68°<ref>{{Cite web |title=HUAWEI Mate 40 debuts with curved display, Kirin 9000 SoC and 50MP camera |url=https://pocketnow.com/huawei-mate-40-debuts-with-curved-display-kirin-9000-soc-and-50mp-camera |access-date=2022-01-26 |work=pocketnow.com |language=en |quote=The Mate 40 features a 6.5-inch Flex OLED display with a 2376 x 1080-pixel resolution and 68-degree curved display. |archive-date=2022-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220209011253/https://pocketnow.com/huawei-mate-40-debuts-with-curved-display-kirin-9000-soc-and-50mp-camera |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而另外的三款同系列手机则均采用与[[华为Mate_30系列|华为Mate 30系列]]相似的88°“超曲环幕屏”<ref name=":8" />。与其前代手机不同的是，在Mate 30 Pro上取消实体音量键受到消费者消极反馈后<ref>{{Cite web |title=New Update For Huawei Mate 30 Pro 5G Fixes Inconsistent Virtual Volume Control |url=https://seogoog.com/new-update-for-huawei-mate-30-pro-5g-fixes-inconsistent-virtual-volume-control/ |access-date=2020-10-24 |work=Seogoog |language=en-US |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122062439/https://seogoog.com/new-update-for-huawei-mate-30-pro-5g-fixes-inconsistent-virtual-volume-control/ |archive-date=2020-11-22 |dead-url=no |quote=……with a pretty curved display called Horizon Display. As part of the design changes made because of the screen, Huawei let go of the physical volume buttons and replaced them with a virtual volume rocker that can be controlled from any side of the screen. However, some users have reported issues when using this virtual volume buttons. }}</ref>，华为在Mate 40系列上保留了实体的音量键，但沿用了Mate 30系列的红色实体电源按键<ref>{{Cite web |title=Here’s our first look at Huawei’s Mate 40 Pro |url=https://www.theverge.com/2020/10/23/21529915/huawei-mate-40-pro-hands-on |access-date=2020-10-24 |date=2020-10-23 |last=Byford |first=Sam |work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]] |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101114437/https://www.theverge.com/2020/10/23/21529915/huawei-mate-40-pro-hands-on |archive-date=2020-11-01 |dead-url=no |quote=……Unlike