华为Mate 40系列搭载[[海思半導體|海思]]麒麟9000系列[[单片系统|SoC]]芯片。美國科技媒體Android Authority記者哈德利·西蒙斯認爲受[[中美贸易战|中美贸易战]]的影响，华为被[[美国|美国]]在芯片方面制裁，因此华为Mate 40系列有可能是最后一个基于麒麟SoC的旗舰手机系列<ref name=":2">{{Cite web |title=Huawei Mate 40 series announced: The last Kirin-powered flagship |url=https://www.androidauthority.com/huawei-mate-40-pro-1126805/ |access-date=2020-10-24 |date=2020-10-22 |work=Android Authority |language=en-US |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200612104303/https://www.androidauthority.com/huawei-mate-40-pro-1126805/ |archive-date=2020-06-12 |dead-url=no |quote=The US trade ban means that the Mate 40 series will be the last flagship to be powered by Kirin chips, at least for a while. }}</ref>。

Mate 40搭载麒麟9000E SoC芯片，而2020年发布的该系列其余手机均搭载麒麟9000 SoC芯片。2022年发布的Mate 40E Pro则搭载了麒麟9000L芯片。该系列芯片基于[[台灣積體電路製造|台积电]]5[[纳米|纳米]]工艺制造<ref>{{Cite web |title=TSMC's 5nm process out of stock for Kirin 9000, Huawei's contract loss costing big to Taiwanese chip maker |url=https://www.huaweicentral.com/tsmcs-5nm-process-out-of-stock-for-kirin-9000-huaweis-contract-loss-costing-big-to-taiwanese-chip-maker/ |access-date=2021-07-01 |date=2021-04-21 |last=Sarkar |first=Amy |work=Huawei Central |language=en-US |quote=With the deadline of September 15, 2020, Huawei’s Kirin 9000 processor was out of print TSMC 5nm process. |archive-date=2021-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421055059/https://www.huaweicentral.com/tsmcs-5nm-process-out-of-stock-for-kirin-9000-huaweis-contract-loss-costing-big-to-taiwanese-chip-maker/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，9000及9000E拥有153亿个晶体管，比[[Apple_A14|Apple A14]]多30%，均搭载基于[[ARM_Cortex-A77|ARM Cortex-A77]]与[[ARM_Cortex-A55|ARM Cortex-A55]]的8核[[CPU|CPU]]与[[Mali_(GPU)|Mali-G78]] [[GPU|GPU]]<ref>{{Cite web |title=Huawei Kirin 9000 announced: first 5G 5nm chip with a CPU and GPU that may put it at a disadvantage |url=https://www.phonearena.com/news/huawei-kirin-9000-5nm-5g-soc_id128007 |access-date=2020-10-24 |last=Hamid |first=Anam |work=Phone Arena |language=en-US |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201103151730/https://www.phonearena.com/news/huawei-kirin-9000-5nm-5g-soc_id128007 |archive-date=2020-11-03 |dead-url=no |quote=Huawei took a swipe at Apple by revealing that its flagship chip has 15.3 billion transistors, 30 percent more than Apple's A14 Bionic chip……Instead, it has one Cortex-A77 core clocked at 3.13 GHz, three Cortex-A77 cores with clock speeds of 2.54 GHz, and four Cortex-A55 cores running at 2.05 GHz. }}</ref>。而麒麟9000L则由8核CPU减少至6核CPU<ref name="gizmochina-mate40epro">{{Cite web |title=Huawei Mate 40E Pro 5G powered by Kirin 9000L SoC goes on sale for 6,700 yuan ($1,062) |url=https://www.gizmochina.com/2022/02/28/huawei-mate-40e-pro-5g-launched-china/ |access-date=2022-02-28 |date=2022-02-28 |last=Jeet |work=Gizmochina |language=en-US |archive-date=2022-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220228151244/https://www.gizmochina.com/2022/02/28/huawei-mate-40e-pro-5g-launched-china/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。麒麟9000搭载24核GPU，而麒麟9000E与麒麟9000L搭载22核GPU<ref name=":10">{{Cite web |title=Huawei Kirin 9000 Vs Kirin 9000E - What's the difference? |url=https://www.gizchina.com/2020/10/25/huawei-kirin-9000-vs-kirin-9000e-whats-the-difference/ |access-date=2021-07-01 |date=2020-10-25 |work=Gizchina.com |language=en-US |quote=However, while the Kirin 9000 uses a 24-core version, the Kirin 9000E has 22 cores……In addition, the NPU part of Kirin 9000 uses a combination of 2 large cores + 1 micro core. However, the Kirin 9000E is a combination of 1 large core + 1 micro core. |archive-date=2020-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201229221030/https://www.gizchina.com/2020/10/25/huawei-kirin-9000-vs-kirin-9000e-whats-the-difference/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="gizmochina-mate40epro" />。在自研[[神经网络处理器|NPU]]方面，其使用华为自研第二代达芬奇架构<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://kns.cnki.net/kcms/detail/detail.aspx?doi=10.28659/n.cnki.nrmyd.2020.003046&dbcode=CCND |title=华为Mate40系列为何遭抢购？ |author=姚春鸽 |work=人民邮电 |date=2020-11-10 |accessdate=2021-07-01 |language=zh |doi=10.28659/n.cnki.nrmyd.2020.003046 |quote=NPU则采用华为自研第二代达芬奇架构，…… |archive-date=2021-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210829123346/https://kns.cnki.net/kcms/detail/detail.aspx?doi=10.28659%2Fn.cnki.nrmyd.2020.003046&dbcode=CCND |dead-url=no }}</ref>，麒麟9000搭载两个大核和一个微核，麒麟9000E与麒麟9000L搭载一个大核和一个微核<ref name=":10" />。麒麟9000系列也内置[[海思半導體|巴龙5000]]基带芯片<ref>{{Cite web |title=Huawei unveils the Kirin 9000 & Kirin 9000E chipsets, its first 5G-integrated 5nm SoCs |url=https://www.gizmochina.com/2020/10/22/huawei-unveils-the-kirin-9000-chipset-its-first-5g-integrated-5nm-soc/ |access-date=2020-10-24 |date=2020-10-22 |last=Ikoba |first=Jed John |work=Gizmochina |language=en-US |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214041141/https://www.gizmochina.com/2020/10/22/huawei-unveils-the-kirin-9000-chipset-its-first-5g-integrated-5nm-soc/ |archive-date=2020-12-14 |dead-url=no |quote=In other respects, the two chipsets seem to be the same, including the integration of Balong 5000 5G baseband,…… }}</ref>，其5G版本支持[[5G|5G网络]]，而其后华为发布的Mate 40 Pro 4G版本亦搭载了麒麟9000芯片，但该版本的处理器不支持5G<ref>{{Cite web |title=HUAWEI Quietly Launches A New HUAWEI Mate 40 Pro 4G With HarmonyOS 2.0 – Pokde.Net |url=https://pokde.net/gadget/smartphone/huawei-mate-40-pro-4g-harmonyos-2-0 |access-date=2021-05-15 |language=en-US |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426152212/https://pokde.net/gadget/smartphone/huawei-mate-40-pro-4g-harmonyos-2-0 |archive-date=2021-04-26 |dead-url=no |quote=……the new HUAWEI Mate 40 Pro 4G comes with the same features and specs as the previously launched HUAWEI Mate 40 Pro minus the 5G connectivity, despite touting the same Kirin 9000 chipset. }}</ref>，有可能是因为美国制裁升级导致<ref>{{Cite web |title=麒麟绝版?华为官网:Mate 40 Pro 4G版麒麟9000处理器（上市时间及价格未定）-电子工程专辑 |url=https://www.eet-china.com/kj/63146.html |access-date=2021-05-15 |work=www.eet-china.com |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210515133236/https://www.eet-china.com/kj/63146.html |archive-date=2021-05-15 |dead-url=no |quote=……同时这些芯片都是2020年提前生产好的芯片，加上海思麒麟9000是一颗集成基带的处理器，这或许意味着海思麒麟9000内部的5G基带因为禁令的进一部升级而浪费了。 }}</ref>。2021年3月10日宣布的Mate 40E 5G手机则搭载麒麟990E 5G芯片<ref>{{Cite web |title=Huawei Mate 40E, with Kirin 990E chipset, goes official |url=https://in.finance.yahoo.com/news/huawei-mate-40e-kirin-990e-063807622.html |access-date=2021-03-11 |work=in.finance.yahoo.com |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316124616/https://in.finance.yahoo.com/news/huawei-mate-40e-kirin-990e-063807622.html |archive-date=2021-03-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，该芯片曾在华为Mate 30E Pro上首发搭载<ref>{{Cite web |title=Mate 30E Pro 5G低调发布：换装麒麟990E、去美化？ - Huawei 华为 |url=http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1044017.htm |access-date=2021-07-01 |last=cnBeta |work=cnBeta.COM |language=zh-CN |quote=处理器不是麒麟990 5G，而是第一次出现的麒麟990E 5G…… |archive-date=2020-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101212621/https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1044017.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，采用7nm工艺制造，其CPU与麒麟990系列相同，但GPU性能略逊一筹，也具有与麒麟990系列一样的NPU和升级款的基带<ref>{{Cite web |title=How the Kirin 990E 5G differs from the Kirin 990 and Kirin 990 5G |url=https://www.gizmochina.com/2020/10/24/how-the-kirin-990e-5g-differs-from-the-kirin-990-and-kirin-990-5g/ |access-date=2021-03-11 |date=2020-10-24 |work=Gizmochina |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201229231446/https://www.gizmochina.com/2020/10/24/how-the-kirin-990e-5g-differs-from-the-kirin-990-and-kirin-990-5g/ |archive-date=2020-12-29 |dead-url=no |last1=Onawole |first1=Habeeb |quote=As you can see, the new Kirin 990E 5G processor offers the same CPU performance as the Kirin 990 5G. However, its GPU is not as powerful as that of the Kirin 990  and Kirin 990 5G……Huawei also seems to have slightly upgraded the modem of the Kirin 990E 5G. }}</ref>，2021年6月29日上架的该型号4G版本则没有5G功能。

华为Mate 40采用6.5英寸的FHD+ [[有機發光二極體|OLED]]屏幕，分辨率2376x1080<ref name=":1" />；而该系列其他手机均采用6.76英寸FHD+ OLED屏幕，分辨率2772x1344<ref>{{Cite web |title=Huawei Mate 40 release date, price, news and features |url=https://www.techradar.com/news/huawei-mate-40-news |access-date=2020-10-24 |last=October 2020 |first=James Rogerson 22 |work=TechRadar |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119075122/https://www.techradar.com/news/huawei-mate-40-news |archive-date=2020-11-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。所有屏幕均支持240Hz触控采样率和90Hz刷新率<ref>{{Cite web |title=Huawei Mate 40 brings 6.5-inch OLED, triple camera and Kirin 9000E |url=https://www.gsmarena.com/the_huawei_mate_40_has_smaller_screen_and_battery_fewer_cameras_but_is_still_a_pro-news-45927.php |access-date=2021-07-01 |work=GSMArena.com |language=en-US |quote=You still get 90Hz refresh rate, 240Hz touch sampling and most importantly, it's still an OLED. |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204105633/https://www.gsmarena.com/the_huawei_mate_40_has_smaller_screen_and_battery_fewer_cameras_but_is_still_a_pro-news-45927.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

华为Mate 40系列均搭载屏下光学指纹识别，Mate 40搭载2D人脸识别，该系列其他手机均支持3D人脸识别<ref>{{Cite web |title=Huawei Mate 40 Pro rumoured to use 3D face recognition for payments |url=https://www.gizmochina.com/2020/07/01/huawei-mate-40-pro-3d-face-recognition-payments/ |access-date=2020-10-25 |date=2020-07-01 |last=Jeet |work=Gizmochina |language=en-US |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120071232/https://www.gizmochina.com/2020/07/01/huawei-mate-40-pro-3d-face-recognition-payments/ |archive-date=2020-11-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Mate 40全系支持[[近場通訊|NFC]]。Mate 40搭载Z轴线性马达，而该系列其余手机均搭载X轴线性马达<ref>{{Cite web |title=Huawei Mate 40 Pro, Pro+ and RS unveiled with 5nm chipsets, amazing camera setups |url=https://www.gsmarena.com/huawei_mate_40_pro_pro_and_rs_unveiled_with_676_90_hz_displays_50_mp_main_camera-news-45926.php |access-date=2020-10-24 |work=GSMArena.com |language=en-US |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123133803/https://www.gsmarena.com/huawei_mate_40_pro_pro_and_rs_unveiled_with_676_90_hz_displays_50_mp_main_camera-news-45926.php |archive-date=2020-11-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

续航方面，华为Mate 40搭载4200mAh电池<ref>{{Cite web |title=Huawei Mate 40 battery |url=https://www.kimovil.com/en/huawei-mate-40/battery |access-date=2020-10-25 |last=Kimovil.com |work=Kimovil.com |language=en |archive-url=https://archive.today/20201212100105/https://www.kimovil.com/en/huawei-mate-40/battery |archive-date=2020-12-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，该系列其他手机均搭载4400mAh电池<ref>{{Cite web |title=Huawei Mate 40 Pro battery |url=https://www.kimovil.com/en/huawei-mate-40-pro/battery |access-date=2020-10-25 |last=Kimovil.com |work=Kimovil.com |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316124618/https://www.kimovil.com/en/huawei-mate-40-pro/battery |archive-date=2021-03-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Mate 40搭载40W有线快速充电，不支持[[無線充電|无线充电]]；而该系列其他手机均支持66W的有线快充及50W的无线快充<ref>{{Cite web |title=Huawei’s Mate 40 Pro announced with speedy 50W wireless charging |url=https://www.theverge.com/2020/10/22/21528249/huawei-mate-40-pro-plus-release-date-news-features-price-specs-cameras |access-date=2020-10-24 |date=2020-10-22 |last=Porter |first=Jon |work=The Verge |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101015359/https://www.theverge.com/2020/10/22/21528249/huawei-mate-40-pro-plus-release-date-news-features-price-specs-cameras |archive-date=2020-11-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。华为Mate 40具有[[国际防护等级认证|IP53]]防尘防水等级<ref name=":1" />，其余三款型号则具有IP68防塵防水等級<ref name=":4" /><ref name=":5" /><ref name=":6" />。

华为Mate 40系列亦兼容华为后续发布的M-Pencil第二代<ref>{{Cite web |title=The Huawei M-Pencil 2 is compatible with the Mate 40 series |url=https://www.gizmochina.com/2021/07/04/the-huawei-m-pencil-2-is-compatible-with-the-mate-40-series/ |access-date=2021-07-19 |date=2021-07-04 |last=Onawole |first=Habeeb |work=Gizmochina |language=en-US |archive-date=2021-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210720141721/https://www.gizmochina.com/2021/07/04/the-huawei-m-pencil-2-is-compatible-with-the-mate-40-series/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 软件 ==
华为Mate 40系列出厂搭载基于[[Android_10|Android 10]]的[[EMUI|EMUI]]11，其于2020年华为全球开发者大会上发布，支持多样息屏显示、回复消息悬浮窗、地震预警、多屏协同、AI系统级翻译等新特性<ref>{{Cite web |title=EMUI 11 - 华为官网 |url=https://consumer.huawei.com/cn/emui-11/?fromConsumer=cn_homepage_EMUI%2011 |access-date=2020-11-19 |work=华为官网 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20201212101833/https://consumer.huawei.com/cn/emui-11/?fromConsumer=cn_homepage_EMUI%2011 |archive-date=2020-12-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而中国大陆版的Mate 40系列则是全球首款支持[[數字人民幣|數字人民幣]]硬件錢包的智能手機，支持收付雙方設備無需網絡即可交易的“雙離線交易”<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://china.hket.com/article/2790379/%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%BE%EF%BC%81%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BAMate%2040%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%97%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E7%A1%AC%E4%BB%B6%E9%8C%A2%E5%8C%85%20%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E5%8F%AF%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93 |title=全球首款！華為Mate 40支持數字人民幣硬件錢包 無網絡可交易 |work=香港經濟日報 |date=2020-10-31 |accessdate=2020-10-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129130039/https://china.hket.com/article/2790379/%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%BE%EF%BC%81%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BAMate%2040%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%97%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E7%A1%AC%E4%BB%B6%E9%8C%A2%E5%8C%85%20%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E5%8F%AF%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93 |archivedate=2020-11-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

