2020年10月23日全球发布会结束后，中国大陆电商平台[[京东商城|京东商城]]启动Mate 40 Pro预售，仅28秒售罄；作为对比，[[IPhone_12|iPhone 12系列]]在同平台的首销售罄时间为30秒<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.globaltimes.cn/content/1204471.shtml |title=Huawei Mate 40 phones sell out in 28 seconds, faster than iPhone 12 |work=[[环球时报|Global Times]] |date=2020-10-24 |accessdate=2020-11-20 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101125127/https://www.globaltimes.cn/content/1204471.shtml |archivedate=2020-11-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2020年10月30日中国大陆发布会结束后，Mate 40系列在[[京东商城|京东商城]]上首销，仅用11秒便售罄<ref name=":7">{{Cite news |url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_9788614 |title=华为Mate40系列开售，“11秒售罄” |author=肖皓月 |work=红星新闻 |date=2020-10-30 |author2=杨程 |via=澎湃新闻 |accessdate=2020-11-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127121420/https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_9788614 |archivedate=2020-11-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。华为将其被美国制裁而缺少的麒麟芯片作为卖点进行宣传，以“绝唱”形容Mate 40系列，达到了较好的营销效果<ref name=":9" />。

由于受到[[美国|美国]]的半导体制裁，华为消费者业务总裁余承东表示Mate 40系列在中国大陆以外地区发布后的预订量已超过华为的供应能力，正抓紧生产，华为也在“想尽各种办法解决供应难题”<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.wenweipo.com/a/202010/30/AP5f9c19bfe4b00c53d99972e2.html |title=華為旗艦產品Mate40系列國內正式發布 售價較國外低三成 |author=何花 |work=香港文匯網 |date=2020-10-30 |author2=毛麗娟 |accessdate=2020-11-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127041209/https://www.wenweipo.com/a/202010/30/AP5f9c19bfe4b00c53d99972e2.html |archivedate=2020-11-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。如香港在2020年11月27日上市，只推出Mate 40 Pro一款型號<ref>{{Cite web |title=壓軸旗艦 Huawei Mate 40 Pro 香港賣街 - DCFever.com |url=https://www.dcfever.com/news/readnews.php?id=29426 |access-date=2020-11-27 |date=2020-11-27 |work=DCFever |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205080506/https://www.dcfever.com/news/readnews.php?id=29426 |archive-date=2020-12-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年12月曾传出Mate 40 Pro+停产的消息，但随后被华为官方否认<ref>{{Cite web |title=Huawei Mate 40 Pro +: the company denies the stop to production |url=https://en.gizchina.it/2020/12/huawei-mate-40-pro-plus-stop-production/ |access-date=2020-12-12 |date=2020-12-06 |work=GizChina.it |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210515133236/https://en.gizchina.it/2020/12/huawei-mate-40-pro-plus-stop-production/ |archive-date=2021-05-15 |dead-url=no |last1=Perrone |first1=Michele }}</ref>。

由于受到美国制裁，华为手机不能在美国销售<ref>{{Cite web |title=Huawei teases US consumers with Black Friday 100 per cent discount offer |url=https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3157228/huawei-banned-us-teases-consumers-black-friday-100-cent-discount |access-date=2021-11-29 |date=2021-11-24 |work=South China Morning Post |language=en |archive-date=2022-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220209011929/https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3157228/huawei-banned-us-teases-consumers-black-friday-100-cent-discount |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但与华为关系密切的鼎桥通信（TD Tech）<ref>{{Cite web |title=Huawei might have found a way around the US ban – Phandroid |url=https://phandroid.com/2021/11/19/huawei-might-have-found-a-way-around-the-us-ban/ |access-date=2021-11-29 |date=2021-11-19 |work=phandroid.com |language=en-US |archive-date=2022-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220209010542/https://phandroid.com/2021/11/19/huawei-might-have-found-a-way-around-the-us-ban/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>可能绕过美国禁令，在美国销售与Mate 40系列同规格的“鼎桥 Mate 40系列”<ref>{{Cite web |title=Huawei Mate 40 Pro to be rebranded by TD Tech to possibly sell in the US |url=https://www.techradar.com/news/huawei-mate-40-pro-to-be-rebranded-by-td-tech-to-possibly-sell-in-the-us |access-date=2021-11-29 |date=2021-11-09 |last=updated |first=David Lumb last |work=TechRadar |language=en |archive-date=2022-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220209010625/https://www.techradar.com/news/huawei-mate-40-pro-to-be-rebranded-by-td-tech-to-possibly-sell-in-the-us |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=TD Tech to relaunch the Huawei Mate 40 Pro to circumvent US sanctions |url=https://www.notebookcheck.net/TD-Tech-to-relaunch-the-Huawei-Mate-40-Pro-to-circumvent-US-sanctions.578119.0.html |access-date=2021-11-29 |last=Alderson |first=Alex |work=Notebookcheck |language=en |archive-date=2022-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220209010617/https://www.notebookcheck.net/TD-Tech-to-relaunch-the-Huawei-Mate-40-