=== 正面评价 ===
[[Engadget|Engadget]]的丹尼尔·库柏（Daniel Cooper）赞赏了华为Mate 40 Pro的AI摄影大师功能，认为这个功能很适合静物和明亮场景的拍摄。与[[iPhone_12|iPhone 12]]的夜景拍摄相比，牺牲了准确性，但将捕捉到的全部细节都增强展示了出来<ref name=":8">{{Cite web |title=Huawei’s Mate 40 Pro is another powerful flagship that you won't buy |url=https://www.engadget.com/huawei-mate-40-123031700.html |access-date=2020-11-19 |work=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128195038/https://www.engadget.com/huawei-mate-40-123031700.html |archive-date=2020-11-28 |dead-url=no |quote=the camera, co-developed with Leica,……,I shot plenty of images in the 50-megapixel AI “Ultra Clarity” mode to see what this phone could do. This mode is designed to shoot stills of objects and scenery in good light,……, Compare that to, say, the iPhone 12, and Huawei's approach sacrifices accuracy in favor of just latching onto any detail it can and amplifying it as much as possible. }}</ref>。手机的外观也得到了肯定，Android Authority的瑞恩-托马斯·肖（Ryan-Thomas Shaw）很欣赏手机的外观，Pro和Pro+正面的超曲环幕屏设计在视觉上消除了边框的存在。背面采用AG磨砂玻璃工艺经阳光照射时，会呈现出彩色的光纹<ref name=":02">{{Cite web |title=Huawei Mate 40 Pro review: The full hardware package |url=https://www.androidauthority.com/huawei-mate-40-pro-review-1170941/ |access-date=2020-11-19 |date=2020-11-03 |work=Android Authority |language=en-US |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121034120/https://www.androidauthority.com/huawei-mate-40-pro-review-1170941/ |archive-date=2020-11-21 |dead-url=no |quote=The curved glass edges on both front and back contribute to a sleek, elegant-looking device with thin bezels and minimal rails. }}</ref>。瑞恩和腾讯科技认为华为Mate 40 Pro的充电速度表现出色，在腾讯科技的测评中华为Mate 40 Pro的66W单电芯电池快充速度和[[OPPO_Find_X2|OPPO Find X2 Pro]]的65W双电芯快充的速度几乎持平，远领先于同为单电芯[[小米10|小米10 Pro]]的50W快充<ref>{{Cite web |title=华为Mate 40 Pro评测：你想知道的，这里都有解答 |url=https://tech.qq.com/a/20201030/012599.htm |access-date=2020-11-21 |work=腾讯科技 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206171642/https://tech.qq.com/a/20201030/012599.htm |archive-date=2020-12-06 |dead-url=no |quote=最终的结果是华为Mate40 Pro整体的充电速度和OPPO 65W的双电芯VOOC闪充几乎相差无几，都是在41分钟左右充满，华为比OPPO稍慢但可以忽略，小米10 Pro的50W充电速度第三…… }}</ref>。瑞恩还指出电池续航表现也很出色，基本能满足日常场景一天的需求<ref name=":02" />。多家媒体都认为麒麟9000芯片在安卓阵容足够出色，性能上领先于同期的高通芯片<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://mobile.zol.com.cn/755/7553836.html |title=不负“华为最强芯”之名 一文看懂麒麟9000强在何处 |publisher=中关村在线 |date=2021-06-15 |accessdate=2021-06-15 |author1=阿喾 |archive-date=2020-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201000656/http://mobile.zol.com.cn/755/7553836.html |dead-url=no |quote=如今，麒麟9000在5G、AI、GPU、ISP影像等方面相较上一代都有了全方位的升级，这样的提升或许只能用“飞跃”来形容了，…… }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://m.k.sohu.com/d/491512920 |title=麒麟9000芯片性能出炉：力压高通骁龙，但仍不如苹果A13 |publisher=搜狐新闻 |date=2020-10-24 |accessdate=2021-06-15 |author1=Tech情报局 |archive-date=2021-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210616042953/https://m.k.sohu.com/d/491512920 |dead-url=no |quote=外媒也第一时间测试了它的实际性能对比，以所搭载的华为Mate40 Pro为代表机型，在GeekBench的多核CPU测试中，性能跑分3704。这一跑分结果居于目前最高。排在第二位的则是搭载A13芯片的iPhone11 Pro Max，而搭载 高通骁龙865+芯片的则普遍在3300分左右。可以看出，麒麟9000芯片性能力压高通骁龙865+，多核也超过了苹果A13。 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1074095.htm |title=麒麟9000芯片有多强？让华为Mate40 Pro+来告诉你 |publisher=cnBeta |date=2021-01-05 |accessdate=2021-06-15 |author1=PCPOP |archive-date=2021-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210616043329/https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1074095.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 负面评价 ===
[[The_Next_Web|The Next Web]]的纳皮尔·洛佩兹（Napier Lopez）认为现在华为Mate 40系列对于海外华为粉丝来说是一个糟糕的选择，尽管华为在硬件上毫不逊色[[苹果|苹果]]和[[三星Galaxy|三星]]，但是[[国家安全|国家安全]]问题以及[[Google流动服务|GMS]]服务的缺少令人担忧<ref>{{Cite web |title=Huawei’s Mate 40 Pro looks like one of the best phones people won’t buy |url=https://thenextweb.com/plugged/2020/10/23/huaweis-mate-40-pro-looks-like-one-of-the-best-phones-you-probably-cant-buy/ |access-date=2020-11-19 |date=2020-10-23 |last=Lopez |first=Napier |work=Plugged {{!}} The Next Web |language=en-us |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109212042/https://thenextweb.com/plugged/2020/10/23/huaweis-mate-40-pro-looks-like-one-of-the-best-phones-you-probably-cant-buy/ |archive-date=2020-11-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。The Register的马修·休斯（Matthew Hughes）还指出在[[AppGallery|华为应用市场]]内不仅有些软件无法下载而且搜索结果混乱，例如搜索[[Twitter|Twitter]]结果会弹出一个推特網站的链接和各种毫不相关的应用推荐（[[Snapchat|Snapchat]]和[[TikTok|TikTok]]甚至已经停止运营的[[Vine|Vine]]）；对于无法下载的软件，消费者可以向华为官方发送软件添加请求，或者通过第三方的[[APK|APK]][[镜像网站|镜像网站]]去下载自己想要的[[App|App]]<ref>{{Cite web |title=The Huawei Mate 40 Pro would be the best Android flagship on the market – were it not for the US-China trade war |url=https://www.theregister.com/2020/11/02/huawei_mate_40_pro_review/ |access-date=2020-11-19 |last=Hughes |first=Matthew |work=www.theregister.com |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210115113/https://www.theregister.com/2020/11/02/huawei_mate_40_pro_review/ |archive-date=2020-12-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Engadget|Engadget中文版]]同样表示即使华为推出[[华为移动服务|HMS]]服务来弥补，但目前在国外市场取得效果甚微，短时间并不能替代谷歌服务<ref>{{Cite web |title=華為 Mate 40 系列登場，搭載麒麟 9000 的品牌高階晶片絕唱 |url=https://cn.engadget.com/huawei-mate-40-133548286.html |access-date=2020-11-21 |work=cn.engadget.com |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208124702/https://cn.engadget.com/huawei-mate-40-133548286.html |archive-date=2020-12-08 |dead-url=no |author1=Sanji Feng }}</ref>。[[CNET|CNET]]则引用台湾[[电子时报|电子时报]]的一份预测报告表明<ref>{{Cite web |title=Global smartphone shipments to see double-digit growth in 2021, says Digitimes Research |url=https://www.digitimes.com/news/a20201007PD212.html |access-date=2020-11-19 |work=DIGITIMES |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206134846/https://www.digitimes.com/news/a20201007PD212.html |archive-date=2020-12-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2021年4月，华为的手机出货量可能因为[[美國對中華人民共和國的制裁|美国制裁]]的影响降至第七位，并认为华为Mate 40 Pro将是华为在智能手机领域的“最后一搏”<ref>{{Cite web |title=Huawei's Mate 40 Pro could be firm's last hurrah in the smartphone world |url=https://www.cnet.com/news/huaweis-mate-40-pro-could-be-its-last-hurrah-in-smartphone-world/ |access-date=2020-11-19 |last=Collins |first=Katie |work=CNET |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127194402/https://www.cnet.com/news/huaweis-mate-40-pro-could-be-its-last-hurrah-in-smartphone-world/ |archive-date=2020-11-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

